ls -l → files aur folders ki detail list


“long format” – ye ls command ke saath use hota hai aur extra details dikhata hai, sirf file/folder ke naam ke bajaye.

Example:

Command:

ls -l

Output (example):

drwxr-xr-x 2 kali kali 4096 Apr 10 14:51 Desktop
-rw-r--r-- 1 kali kali  142 Apr 10 14:51 file.txt
Explanation of columns:

drwxr-xr-x → permissions (kaun read/write/execute kar sakta hai)

2 → number of links

kali → owner

kali → group

4096 → file/folder size (bytes)

Apr 10 14:51 → creation/modification date

Desktop / file.txt → file/folder name

✅ Short me:
-l = detailed information display

Without -l:

ls

Sirf file/folder ke naam dikhenge.

With -l:

ls -l

File/folder ke permissions, owner, size, date aur name sab dikhega.


Don Bhai😡, chalo main aapko ye lambi line step by step detail me samjhata hoon:

Line jo aap ne di:

drwxr-xr-x 2 kali kali 4096 Apr 10 14:51 Downloads

Ye ls -l ka output hai, jo directory aur file ke bare me poori detail deta hai.

1️⃣ drwxr-xr-x → Permissions

d → iska matlab hai ye directory hai

Agar file hoti → - dikhata

rwx (owner ke liye) → owner (yaha kali) ke liye read, write, execute permissions

r-x (group ke liye) → group ke users ke liye read aur execute, write nahi

r-x (others ke liye) → baaki sab ke liye read aur execute, write nahi

Shortcut:

r = read (dekh sakte ho)

w = write (edit / delete kar sakte ho)

x = execute (folder me enter kar sakte ho / file run kar sakte ho)

2️⃣ 2 → Number of links

Ye directory ke links ya subfolders ko represent karta hai.

Directory me . aur .. links included hote hain.

3️⃣ kali → Owner

Ye folder ka owner user hai, jo yaha kali hai.

4️⃣ kali → Group

Ye folder ka group hai, jo yaha bhi kali hai.

Group ke users ke permissions r-x set hai.

5️⃣ 4096 → File size (bytes)

Directory ka size 4096 bytes hai (Linux me har folder ka default block size 4KB hota hai)

6️⃣ Apr 10 14:51 → Last modification date & time

Folder last kab modify hua ye dikhata hai.

7️⃣ Downloads → Folder name

Ye actual folder ka naam hai.

✅ Summary (Simplified)
Field	Matlab
d	Directory
rwxr-xr-x	Permissions (owner/group/others)
2	Number of links
kali	Owner
kali	Group
4096	Size in bytes
Apr 10 14:51	Last modified date & time
Downloads	Folder name

Matlab: Ye lambi line aapko folder ka full status batati hai: kaun use kar sakta hai, owner kaun hai, size kya hai, last kab change hua, aur folder ka naam


