Linux me prompt me ye symbols aur user/folder info badal bhi sakte hain

Example: [user@hostname folder]$ ye common hai, lekin aap apne hisaab se change kar sakte ho

Lekin concept same rehta hai:

user ka naam

machine ka naam

current folder

symbol ($ ya #)

